name: Puffin Rock
overview: Life is sweet on beautiful Puffin Rock, where puffling Oona, her baby brother Baba and their pals learn about nature, friendship and family. Follow the pufflings on their adventures as they explore the wild island!

episodes.name: Puffin Practice
episodes.overview: Oona tries to teach her baby brother Baba how to be a grown-up puffin.

episodes.name: The Mystery Egg
episodes.overview: The kids find a strange egg.

episodes.name: To See the Moon
episodes.overview: Oona wants everyone to see the full moon.

episodes.name: The Shiny Shell
episodes.overview: Oona and Baba attract unwanted attention with a shell.

episodes.name: Friendly Flynne
episodes.overview: Oona and Baba make an unexpected friend.

episodes.name: A Feather Bed
episodes.overview: Oona and Baba search far and wide for new bedding.

episodes.name: Back to the Pond
episodes.overview: The Puffin family guide a friendly frog to the pond.

episodes.name: The Fallen Rocks
episodes.overview: Oona and her pals help free a trapped Bernie.

episodes.name: Homesick Hoglet
episodes.overview: Baba and baby hedgehog Spiky go exploring.

episodes.name: Silky and the Octopus
episodes.overview: Oona and Silky have an octopus adventure!

episodes.name: The Salmon Leap
episodes.overview: Otto tries to get his siblings to fall asleep.

episodes.name: The Great Gull
episodes.overview: Oona and Baba protect a baby seagull from the Great Gull.

episodes.name: Babasitting
episodes.overview: It's spring and Baba wants to wake Spiky from his winter nap!

episodes.name: The Puffin Way
episodes.overview: Oona learns about the slow and steady 'Puffin Way.'

episodes.name: Bernie and the Bee
episodes.overview: Baba and Oona rescue a tired bee.

episodes.name: Find the Owls
episodes.overview: Otto and the puffins search for the hidden Pip and Pop.

episodes.name: Mossy's Flea
episodes.overview: Mossy's flea pal Fred peps up a playdate.

episodes.name: Dinner at Bernie's
episodes.overview: Oona helps Bernie prepare for a special dinner.

episodes.name: Mossy's Mystery
episodes.overview: Mossy is looking forward to the largest berry in the island to ripen but finds out that it has disappeared.

episodes.name: Super Snail
episodes.overview: Baba makes a new friend, a little snail, but when Baba steps away, the snail disappears.
